WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.218 --> 01:43.920
=Episode 5=

01:43.952 --> 01:44.438
(Qiao Lin)

01:44.438 --> 01:44.898
(I'm moving tomorrow.)

01:44.898 --> 01:45.418
(I'll pay you back)

01:45.418 --> 01:45.948
(and send you the new address.)

01:45.948 --> 01:46.384
(Leave me alone!)

01:58.909 --> 01:59.348
Right.

01:59.989 --> 02:00.909
You've never

02:01.549 --> 02:02.868
mentioned you had a cousin.

02:03.549 --> 02:05.348
Should we invite her to our wedding?

02:07.109 --> 02:08.468
She's a distant relative.

02:08.628 --> 02:09.708
We weren't so close.

02:09.989 --> 02:10.748
Never mind.

02:14.960 --> 02:15.468
Alright.

02:15.989 --> 02:16.669
Your call.

02:19.989 --> 02:20.389
Here.

02:30.468 --> 02:32.188
I moved out.

02:33.468 --> 02:34.748
Here's...

02:36.148 --> 02:37.748
(I moved out and canceled the hotel.)

02:38.148 --> 02:38.949
(Here's the money.)

02:43.868 --> 02:46.109
What else do I need?

02:50.069 --> 02:52.069
Can't you take a hint?

02:52.468 --> 02:53.989
Bad sister! Bad Xu Yan!

02:54.229 --> 02:55.468
I'm done with you.

02:59.669 --> 03:01.349
(Lin, I'm sorry.)

03:09.549 --> 03:11.389
(I shouldn't have
let my parents scold you.)

03:11.669 --> 03:12.588
(Come back, please?)

03:12.628 --> 03:13.069
Get lost.

03:15.428 --> 03:15.868
(Get lost.)

03:24.588 --> 03:25.308
Tao.

03:27.269 --> 03:28.868
You're here for Lin?

03:30.069 --> 03:31.588
She's on a business trip to Jingzhou.

03:31.829 --> 03:32.468
Jingzhou?

03:33.628 --> 03:34.628
Didn't she tell you?

03:35.509 --> 03:36.349
Qiao.

03:36.868 --> 03:37.509
Qiao.

03:37.789 --> 03:39.028
Come on, Tao's here.

03:39.148 --> 03:39.789
Look.

03:40.148 --> 03:41.308
Hello, Tao.

03:41.509 --> 03:42.000
Mr. Qiao.

03:42.509 --> 03:43.028
Perfect.

03:43.269 --> 03:44.349
We don't have much work.

03:44.509 --> 03:46.588
Let's go for a drink somewhere.

03:46.949 --> 03:48.069
- Mr. Qiao...
- Drink with him.

03:50.628 --> 03:52.349
Didn't Qiao Lin tell you anything

03:53.109 --> 03:54.628
before she left for Jingzhou?

03:55.829 --> 03:56.669
Did she?

03:56.908 --> 03:58.269
Nothing at all.

03:58.628 --> 03:59.829
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

04:00.389 --> 04:00.949
Well.

04:03.509 --> 04:04.468
We've...

04:06.509 --> 04:07.148
broken up.

04:08.269 --> 04:08.868
What?

04:09.308 --> 04:10.069
I'm sorry.

04:10.188 --> 04:12.588
The number you dialed is unavailable.

04:12.789 --> 04:13.989
Please try again later.

04:15.109 --> 04:15.708
Well?

04:15.989 --> 04:16.752
Can't get through.

04:17.828 --> 04:18.789
She...

04:18.948 --> 04:19.989
She didn't even tell us

04:20.068 --> 04:21.268
about breaking up.

04:21.388 --> 04:22.669
Is she avoiding us?

04:23.149 --> 04:24.068
No way.

04:24.149 --> 04:26.188
Didn't she say she went to
Jingzhou for training?

04:27.188 --> 04:27.669
Jingzhou?

04:27.868 --> 04:29.589
I'll call Qiao Yan right now.

04:29.589 --> 04:30.188
Yeah.

04:32.828 --> 04:34.109
We'll try the clothes later.

04:34.308 --> 04:35.628
I've visited this store.

04:36.068 --> 04:37.508
Try these. Nothing else.

04:39.948 --> 04:41.469
Remember. Stay quiet.

04:41.909 --> 04:42.828
Be polite.

04:43.709 --> 04:44.748
After that,

04:44.948 --> 04:46.109
Haoming's parents

04:46.628 --> 04:47.989
might come home with us.

04:48.508 --> 04:49.268
Once we're back,

04:49.549 --> 04:51.989
tell them you have to meet some friends.

04:52.268 --> 04:52.948
Got it.

04:55.589 --> 04:56.268
So pretty.

04:58.493 --> 05:00.208
(Incoming call from Qiao Jianbin)

05:01.828 --> 05:02.709
Someone's calling.

05:15.068 --> 05:16.909
Sorry, the number you dialed...

05:17.029 --> 05:18.589
- Well?
- She's not answering.

05:19.948 --> 05:20.349
This...

05:20.989 --> 05:21.628
Forget it.

05:22.149 --> 05:24.068
I'll book tickets to Jingzhou now.

05:24.589 --> 05:25.868
Ask your mom

05:26.029 --> 05:27.349
where Qiao Yan lives.

05:27.428 --> 05:28.388
Let's do it now.

05:28.868 --> 05:29.469
Okay.

05:34.349 --> 05:35.589
Is this the place?

05:35.589 --> 05:36.508
So many buildings.

05:36.589 --> 05:37.589
Which one exactly?

05:37.748 --> 05:38.789
How would I know?

05:38.868 --> 05:40.669
This address is from two years ago.

05:40.669 --> 05:41.868
How should I know?

05:41.989 --> 05:42.709
W-What a mess.

05:42.709 --> 05:44.109
Let's try calling Yan again.

05:44.109 --> 05:45.229
She's not answering.

05:45.229 --> 05:46.508
Try it one more time.

05:46.508 --> 05:47.469
Fine, I'll try again.

05:49.308 --> 05:51.508
We just tried on so many dresses.

05:52.748 --> 05:54.029
They all look great.

05:54.149 --> 05:56.989
In the end, it's about
the style you like.

05:58.229 --> 05:58.789
Ms. Yu,

05:59.268 --> 05:59.989
any advice?

06:01.424 --> 06:02.709
For traditional Chinese style,

06:02.709 --> 06:04.508
the Zhou-style Hanfu
with phoenix coronet

06:04.508 --> 06:05.789
and embroidered cape

06:06.188 --> 06:07.308
has majestic patterns

06:07.469 --> 06:08.469
and suits you well.

06:08.789 --> 06:09.669
And it's said

06:09.789 --> 06:11.669
to bring fortune to the bride.

06:12.029 --> 06:13.229
For Western style,

06:13.349 --> 06:14.748
take the last wedding dress

06:14.868 --> 06:16.589
you tried with a very long train.

06:17.188 --> 06:19.109
It looks elegant and graceful.

06:19.828 --> 06:20.909
Check over there.

06:21.669 --> 06:22.508
Don't rush.

06:25.349 --> 06:27.469
In the end, it's about what you prefer.

06:27.789 --> 06:28.709
Qiao Yan.

06:30.388 --> 06:30.989
Yan.

06:32.508 --> 06:33.349
Yan, what's wrong?

06:34.229 --> 06:35.748
- Qiao Yan.
- Yan.

06:46.709 --> 06:47.549
Qiao Yan?

06:48.229 --> 06:49.868
A-Aren't you Xu Yan?

06:52.149 --> 06:53.109
Who are you?

06:53.428 --> 06:54.628
We're her parents.

06:58.789 --> 06:59.909
You're her parents?

06:59.989 --> 07:02.188
Then who are they?

07:03.149 --> 07:03.828
Tell us.

07:04.109 --> 07:04.989
Who are they?

07:05.948 --> 07:06.508
Xu Yan.

07:08.029 --> 07:09.428
Explain this right now.

07:09.709 --> 07:10.428
Ms. Yu,

07:11.229 --> 07:12.469
please let me explain.

07:12.948 --> 07:13.628
I see.

07:14.628 --> 07:15.709
Your name is fake.

07:16.109 --> 07:17.709
Your family background is fake.

07:17.868 --> 07:19.109
So are your parents, huh?

07:19.828 --> 07:20.428
Tell me.

07:20.709 --> 07:21.748
How many more secrets

07:21.828 --> 07:22.948
are you hiding?

07:23.628 --> 07:25.029
We treated you with sincerity,

07:25.469 --> 07:27.469
yet you've fooled our entire family.

07:27.828 --> 07:28.948
Why are you so manipulative?

07:29.229 --> 07:29.989
This is fraud.

07:30.109 --> 07:30.709
Marriage fraud.

07:31.469 --> 07:33.469
This is fraud. Marriage fraud.

07:33.948 --> 07:34.428
Qiao Yan.

07:34.628 --> 07:35.748
What have you done?

07:36.828 --> 07:38.149
What's wrong with you?

07:38.469 --> 07:39.149
Yan.

07:39.508 --> 07:40.789
I'm so disappointed in you.

07:41.469 --> 07:42.589
Stop pestering my son.

07:43.989 --> 07:45.109
You've gone too far.

07:46.388 --> 07:47.120
Haoming, let's go.

07:49.789 --> 07:50.709
We're done.

07:50.868 --> 07:51.428
Haoming.

07:51.868 --> 07:52.628
Don't pester me.

07:57.149 --> 07:58.029
Hurry up.

07:59.549 --> 08:00.229
Don't go.

08:03.748 --> 08:04.388
Haoming.

08:09.868 --> 08:10.428
Yan.

08:11.068 --> 08:11.669
Yan.

08:12.029 --> 08:13.109
"Don't go?"

08:14.388 --> 08:15.868
What's wrong? You seem distracted.

08:18.029 --> 08:18.628
I forgot.

08:19.029 --> 08:20.709
Why are you so jumpy today?

08:21.068 --> 08:23.589
Third Uncle's flight arrives today.

08:24.308 --> 08:25.149
What time?

08:25.428 --> 08:25.948
Five o'clock.

08:26.349 --> 08:27.789
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

08:27.828 --> 08:28.388
Sorry.

08:28.388 --> 08:28.868
I forgot.

08:29.109 --> 08:29.549
Sorry.

08:29.628 --> 08:31.109
We won't come up then.

08:31.229 --> 08:31.508
Okay?

08:31.669 --> 08:33.109
We need to pick up my brother.

08:34.189 --> 08:35.069
Qiao Yan.

08:36.508 --> 08:37.069
It's fine.

08:37.069 --> 08:38.148
I'm so sorry.

08:38.349 --> 08:39.189
Let's hurry then.

08:39.189 --> 08:39.589
Hurry up.

08:39.589 --> 08:39.989
Okay.

08:40.148 --> 08:40.748
I'm so sorry.

08:40.748 --> 08:41.268
No problem.

08:41.388 --> 08:42.628
Yan, walk them out.

08:42.868 --> 08:43.388
Let's go.

08:44.309 --> 08:44.748
Okay.

08:45.589 --> 08:46.189
Let's go.

08:47.229 --> 08:48.069
What's going on?

08:48.229 --> 08:49.628
Let's walk them out.

08:49.628 --> 08:50.788
What's going on here?

08:51.309 --> 08:52.069
Ms. Yu.

08:52.628 --> 08:54.268
I'll pick you up for dinner tomorrow.

08:54.548 --> 08:55.989
I'll call you after work.

08:56.748 --> 08:57.189
Alright.

08:59.989 --> 09:00.709
Mr. Xu, Mrs. Xu.

09:00.709 --> 09:01.268
I have to go.

09:01.309 --> 09:01.709
Okay.

09:02.429 --> 09:02.829
Bye.

09:07.148 --> 09:07.829
Bye.

09:11.309 --> 09:11.829
Qiao Yan.

09:12.709 --> 09:13.788
- Qiao Yan.
- Yan.

09:14.668 --> 09:16.868
That was Mr. Shen

09:16.989 --> 09:18.268
from Jinda Group, right?

09:18.589 --> 09:19.388
How do you know him?

09:20.309 --> 09:22.148
Who was that young man?

09:26.229 --> 09:27.309
You two are...?

09:27.868 --> 09:28.989
We're her parents.

09:29.189 --> 09:30.028
You are...?

09:33.829 --> 09:35.628
We're from the wedding planning company.

09:37.349 --> 09:38.429
Congratulations.

09:38.668 --> 09:39.388
Congratulations.

09:39.508 --> 09:40.268
Those people

09:40.349 --> 09:42.788
are your future in-laws.

09:45.309 --> 09:45.868
Miss Xu.

09:46.069 --> 09:47.028
If there's nothing else,

09:47.109 --> 09:48.709
Ms. Zhang and I will take our leave.

09:49.429 --> 09:50.309
You can transfer

09:50.429 --> 09:51.829
the remaining payment now.

09:52.069 --> 09:53.709
Feel free to contact us anytime.

09:54.748 --> 09:55.268
Let's go.

09:55.309 --> 09:55.989
Okay, Mr. Gao.

09:56.949 --> 09:57.589
Congratulations.

09:58.148 --> 09:58.829
Bye.

09:58.829 --> 09:59.388
Bye.

10:00.189 --> 10:00.668
Let's go.

10:04.069 --> 10:05.989
Yan, what is going on here?

10:10.788 --> 10:11.628
I'm getting married.

10:12.229 --> 10:12.589
What...?

10:14.268 --> 10:15.028
Getting married?

10:15.408 --> 10:15.868
Wait.

10:16.229 --> 10:17.868
Y-You're getting married?

10:17.949 --> 10:19.469
But I don't even know

10:19.508 --> 10:21.229
who my future son-in-law is

10:21.309 --> 10:22.508
or what he looks like.

10:22.709 --> 10:24.508
This is ridiculous.

10:25.229 --> 10:26.748
Aren't you going to tell us

10:27.148 --> 10:28.628
before marrying someone?

10:28.709 --> 10:31.229
Your sister broke off an engagement.

10:31.469 --> 10:32.548
You're getting married.

10:32.868 --> 10:34.349
Neither of you discussed with us.

10:34.469 --> 10:35.709
Are you ignoring us?

10:35.829 --> 10:37.589
You don't need to overreact.

10:37.868 --> 10:39.589
It has nothing to do with you.

10:41.309 --> 10:41.949
What?

10:44.268 --> 10:46.309
I'm not inviting you to my wedding.

10:47.429 --> 10:49.429
Grandma is my only family.

10:53.069 --> 10:54.908
This is outrageous.

10:55.628 --> 10:56.628
Being in the big city

10:56.748 --> 10:59.148
doesn't mean you can look down on us.

11:00.229 --> 11:00.868
Yan.

11:01.868 --> 11:03.829
You've hurt our feelings.

11:04.229 --> 11:05.989
After all, we're your parents.

11:06.069 --> 11:07.189
So what?

11:12.989 --> 11:14.508
You'll never admit you're wrong.

11:15.469 --> 11:18.349
How can children judge their parents?

11:20.148 --> 11:20.829
Fine.

11:21.628 --> 11:23.109
That young man is from

11:23.469 --> 11:24.908
the wealthy Shen family, huh?

11:25.469 --> 11:28.069
He was born with a silver spoon, huh?

11:28.989 --> 11:29.429
Alright.

11:30.148 --> 11:31.788
We won't overreach.

11:32.469 --> 11:33.788
I won't go to your wedding

11:33.989 --> 11:35.668
even if you invite me.

11:36.109 --> 11:37.748
You're no longer my daughter.

11:38.309 --> 11:39.949
Yazhen, let's go find Lin.

11:40.109 --> 11:40.949
Got her address?

11:47.548 --> 11:48.349
I'll send it to you.

11:54.109 --> 11:54.748
Jianbin.

11:58.469 --> 11:59.388
You finally picked up.

11:59.868 --> 12:01.668
I had to switch on my phone.

12:03.388 --> 12:04.208
Where do you live?

12:04.388 --> 12:05.229
Here.

12:07.868 --> 12:08.628
How many bedrooms?

12:09.349 --> 12:10.229
Three.

12:11.429 --> 12:13.109
You live alone in such a big apartment?

12:13.268 --> 12:13.748
No.

12:13.788 --> 12:14.229
Here.

12:14.868 --> 12:16.748
I rented one of the rooms.

12:17.109 --> 12:18.388
The other two rooms

12:18.709 --> 12:20.589
are rented by two other girls.

12:21.109 --> 12:22.388
A shared apartment?

12:22.788 --> 12:23.829
Who are your roommates?

12:24.109 --> 12:25.268
Hello, my lovelies.

12:25.429 --> 12:27.589
Today's another special discount.

12:28.069 --> 12:29.429
Classic soy aroma.

12:30.989 --> 12:31.668
That's it.

12:31.668 --> 12:33.520
Let me chug it down.

12:34.992 --> 12:35.868
Dive in.

12:37.069 --> 12:37.949
No headaches.

12:38.349 --> 12:39.709
Who is that?

12:40.548 --> 12:41.668
She's my roommate.

12:41.788 --> 12:42.429
A livestreamer.

12:44.388 --> 12:45.028
Your room?

12:45.349 --> 12:45.908
Here, Dad.

12:46.148 --> 12:46.548
Not there.

12:46.548 --> 12:47.189
Here.

12:51.949 --> 12:53.469
I apologize.

12:53.469 --> 12:54.349
I'm sorry.

12:54.429 --> 12:56.229
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

12:57.028 --> 12:58.548
It's just that

12:58.589 --> 12:59.949
it happened so suddenly.

12:59.949 --> 13:01.989
I didn't want you to worry.

13:02.268 --> 13:04.589
So I thought I should
get settled here first

13:04.589 --> 13:05.709
before telling you.

13:05.868 --> 13:06.868
Get settled?

13:08.028 --> 13:09.429
This is Jingzhou.

13:10.469 --> 13:12.148
Talented people flock here.

13:12.268 --> 13:14.388
Competition is heated here.

13:14.548 --> 13:15.349
You're here alone,

13:15.388 --> 13:16.268
away from home.

13:16.908 --> 13:19.589
No diplomas, connections, or background.

13:20.589 --> 13:21.949
It's not so easy to live here.

13:22.268 --> 13:23.109
Your dad's right.

13:24.268 --> 13:26.429
You have to let me try first.

13:26.709 --> 13:27.829
Anyway, it's better than

13:27.829 --> 13:29.189
suffering at Lin Tao's home.

13:30.309 --> 13:31.069
Makes sense.

13:32.388 --> 13:34.668
We didn't know
Lin Tao's family was like that.

13:36.349 --> 13:37.148
But Lin,

13:37.508 --> 13:37.949
well...

13:38.589 --> 13:41.709
I still think you should
come home with us.

13:42.349 --> 13:43.349
It's just a town,

13:43.469 --> 13:44.908
but you'll live

13:46.388 --> 13:48.868
a peaceful life with us, right?

13:49.349 --> 13:50.508
Try harder

13:50.788 --> 13:51.868
and be a civil servant.

13:52.028 --> 13:53.709
Make the Lins jealous. Okay?

13:54.949 --> 13:56.548
Civil servant?

13:56.868 --> 13:57.788
You know very well

13:57.788 --> 13:59.229
I was never cut out for studying.

13:59.349 --> 14:00.628
Take the civil service exam?

14:00.829 --> 14:01.388
No way.

14:01.388 --> 14:03.469
Now you admit you're not
cut out for studying?

14:03.868 --> 14:05.668
Who begged us for money

14:05.949 --> 14:07.668
to retake exams to come here?

14:08.069 --> 14:10.949
We didn't even let
Qiao Yan take the exam.

14:11.508 --> 14:12.949
Now you're blaming it on me?

14:13.109 --> 14:14.388
You drove her away, okay?

14:21.709 --> 14:23.548
Do you know that she has a boyfriend?

14:23.709 --> 14:24.589
Forget about it.

14:26.069 --> 14:27.908
We're not even invited to her wedding.

14:28.109 --> 14:28.628
Wedding?

14:30.989 --> 14:31.888
She didn't tell me.

14:32.309 --> 14:32.868
Mom, Dad,

14:33.748 --> 14:36.069
do you want to attend her wedding?

14:38.028 --> 14:38.949
All parents

14:39.668 --> 14:41.668
want to witness
their daughter's wedding.

14:41.748 --> 14:42.628
No, I don't.

14:43.508 --> 14:45.229
She's materialistic and ashamed of us.

14:45.349 --> 14:46.788
She's not my daughter.

14:47.109 --> 14:47.788
Dad.

14:48.268 --> 14:49.788
Yeah, I'm cursing you. So what?

14:50.469 --> 14:51.788
Aren't you ignoring calls

14:51.908 --> 14:53.148
to get compensation?

14:53.709 --> 14:54.949
Go ahead. File a complaint.

14:56.069 --> 14:56.829
The other roommate.

14:57.268 --> 14:57.748
That's it.

15:02.908 --> 15:03.429
Yan.

15:03.668 --> 15:04.589
I'm magnanimous.

15:04.589 --> 15:05.748
I can let it slide.

15:06.429 --> 15:08.508
But it's just angry talk
that Mom and Dad aren't

15:09.309 --> 15:10.829
invited to your wedding, right?

15:11.748 --> 15:13.429
Since they are still here,

15:13.748 --> 15:15.268
let's find a chance

15:15.309 --> 15:17.548
to sit together and clear the air.

15:17.628 --> 15:18.349
What do you think?

15:19.668 --> 15:20.148
Okay.

15:20.748 --> 15:21.388
Okay, right?

15:21.709 --> 15:22.469
I'm coming in.

15:30.709 --> 15:32.508
Who are you looking for?

15:33.829 --> 15:35.229
Isn't this Xu Yan's home?

15:37.349 --> 15:38.469
This is my daughter's home.

15:38.709 --> 15:40.109
Are you her colleague?

15:40.429 --> 15:41.189
Your daughter?

15:41.589 --> 15:43.028
You are...?

15:43.309 --> 15:44.908
We're Yan's parents.

15:45.028 --> 15:46.229
We've been working overseas.

15:46.628 --> 15:48.028
Since Yan's getting married soon,

15:48.229 --> 15:50.109
we came back for her wedding.

15:50.548 --> 15:51.548
She's getting groceries.

15:51.628 --> 15:52.548
She'll be right back.

15:54.628 --> 15:56.229
You're her parents?

15:56.469 --> 15:57.508
You live abroad?

15:58.028 --> 15:59.429
Yeah, w-we work

15:59.429 --> 16:01.028
at a university overseas.

16:02.268 --> 16:02.709
Yan.

16:02.868 --> 16:03.589
Perfect timing.

16:04.109 --> 16:04.949
Your colleague.

16:13.589 --> 16:14.868
Now I get it.

16:15.109 --> 16:16.748
You've been lying all along.

16:17.148 --> 16:18.469
You hired fake parents

16:18.548 --> 16:20.548
and told everyone

16:20.548 --> 16:22.469
that they live abroad.

16:22.949 --> 16:23.668
Yan.

16:29.548 --> 16:30.868
I know exactly what I'm doing.

16:31.028 --> 16:32.069
Thanks for the reminder.

16:32.748 --> 16:34.709
You've got some nerve.

16:34.868 --> 16:37.069
What if the Shen family finds out?

16:37.229 --> 16:38.908
No one will know if you keep quiet.

16:39.309 --> 16:41.028
You'll keep lying to them?

16:41.628 --> 16:42.788
For someone so smart,

16:42.829 --> 16:44.788
why would you do such stupid things?

16:47.069 --> 16:49.349
Once you marry Shen Haoming,

16:49.552 --> 16:50.608
what are you going to do?

16:50.748 --> 16:52.069
Keep lying to him forever?

16:54.508 --> 16:55.908
I'll figure something out.

16:56.388 --> 16:57.268
Not now.

17:01.309 --> 17:02.349
Haoming's mom

17:02.589 --> 17:03.868
looks down on my background.

17:04.709 --> 17:06.108
How else could I marry him?

17:12.788 --> 17:15.189
I've seen the girls she picked for him.

17:16.229 --> 17:17.429
They're all exceptional.

17:18.828 --> 17:20.669
I know you find it despicable.

17:20.869 --> 17:22.308
I admit I'm at fault.

17:23.508 --> 17:24.389
But you don't know

17:25.068 --> 17:26.548
what I've been through,

17:27.028 --> 17:28.348
and can't understand my choices.

17:29.828 --> 17:31.068
All I can say is that

17:31.588 --> 17:33.268
before meeting Shen Haoming,

17:33.669 --> 17:35.149
my life was colorless.

17:35.949 --> 17:36.748
He's the only one

17:36.748 --> 17:38.028
willing to look after me.

17:38.588 --> 17:39.588
The only one.

17:47.748 --> 17:49.229
You may have a thousand excuses,

17:49.348 --> 17:50.629
but lying is wrong.

17:54.229 --> 17:56.189
If I told the truth,

17:57.669 --> 17:59.709
they'd force me to break up with him.

18:00.909 --> 18:02.869
Everything I've worked so hard for

18:04.469 --> 18:05.429
in Jingzhou

18:06.189 --> 18:07.909
would vanish instantly.

18:08.308 --> 18:09.189
Haven't I worked hard?

18:10.268 --> 18:12.068
Yes, I have. But what's the point?

18:16.548 --> 18:17.748
That's why I refuse

18:17.748 --> 18:19.149
to go back to being

18:20.588 --> 18:22.268
that disposable young lady

18:23.788 --> 18:24.949
everyone looked down on.

18:31.949 --> 18:33.709
Life only has a few turning points.

18:34.308 --> 18:35.508
If we seize them,

18:35.949 --> 18:37.909
everything falls into place.

18:38.629 --> 18:40.028
But if we miss those chances,

18:40.268 --> 18:42.229
we can't possibly turn the tide.

18:49.508 --> 18:50.629
Either I lose everything,

18:50.709 --> 18:51.348
or

18:52.508 --> 18:53.389
gain everything.

18:57.869 --> 18:58.629
Do you love him?

18:59.828 --> 19:01.709
Or are you just

19:01.748 --> 19:03.469
a complete fraud after his money?

19:06.348 --> 19:08.028
I want both career and love.

19:09.989 --> 19:12.669
Why do we have to be poor

19:12.669 --> 19:13.748
to prove our love?

19:17.828 --> 19:19.629
If you insist on exposing me...

19:23.248 --> 19:23.918
(Haoming)

19:23.918 --> 19:25.776
(Video Call, Audio Call)

19:32.629 --> 19:33.788
I can't change your mind.

19:34.949 --> 19:37.189
But I can't watch you go down that path.

19:37.869 --> 19:38.828
I won't come again.

20:14.028 --> 20:15.149
(I can't change your mind.)

20:16.308 --> 20:18.629
(But I can't watch you
go down that path.)

20:27.003 --> 20:32.752
(Incoming Call from Shen Haoming)

20:42.229 --> 20:43.149
Hello? What's up?

20:44.028 --> 20:44.508
Yan.

20:45.348 --> 20:47.429
We've confirmed our guest list.

20:47.748 --> 20:49.709
But I took a look at your list.

20:50.508 --> 20:51.989
Your dad, your mom,

20:52.308 --> 20:53.508
Huanhuan, and Mr. Zhou.

20:53.709 --> 20:55.229
Four people. Isn't that too few?

20:57.268 --> 20:59.189
My parents live abroad and rarely

20:59.788 --> 21:01.028
visit any relatives.

21:02.629 --> 21:05.028
If we suddenly reach out
for the wedding,

21:06.068 --> 21:08.348
it'll look like
we're just after gift money.

21:08.629 --> 21:09.149
Right?

21:10.149 --> 21:10.669
Got it.

21:12.389 --> 21:14.308
When are we bringing Grandma over?

21:15.669 --> 21:16.869
Let's bring her here soon.

21:17.189 --> 21:18.869
Let her enjoy her time in Jingzhou.

21:22.548 --> 21:24.308
I'll ask her about it when I go back.

21:25.828 --> 21:27.949
You know she has aged.

21:29.909 --> 21:30.709
I'll go with you.

21:32.548 --> 21:34.348
You have so much work.

21:34.788 --> 21:35.189
Next time,

21:35.508 --> 21:36.788
we'll go together, okay?

21:38.429 --> 21:40.028
I really want to see her.

21:40.748 --> 21:42.588
But I already promised to spend

21:42.588 --> 21:44.108
some days with her this time.

21:44.588 --> 21:46.068
If you come along,

21:46.189 --> 21:47.709
it'll disrupt our plans.

21:47.869 --> 21:48.429
Right?

21:49.588 --> 21:50.149
Got it.

21:50.909 --> 21:52.068
Take care of yourself.

21:52.389 --> 21:52.788
Bye.

21:54.268 --> 21:54.828
Bye.

22:29.675 --> 22:35.632
(Incoming Call from Mom)

22:37.989 --> 22:38.548
What's wrong?

22:39.028 --> 22:39.629
Yan.

22:40.229 --> 22:42.068
Your dad and I have been thinking.

22:42.469 --> 22:44.949
We want to attend your wedding.

22:45.389 --> 22:46.949
That's what your dad said.

22:47.709 --> 22:48.788
No matter what,

22:49.108 --> 22:50.709
you're our daughter.

22:52.229 --> 22:53.548
Got it. Bye.

22:57.488 --> 23:01.392
(Mom)

23:09.008 --> 23:09.501
(Wang Yazhen)

23:24.528 --> 23:28.528
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
too many times笙ｪ

23:30.800 --> 23:34.955
笙ｪI'm giving it all,
just getting nothing back笙ｪ

23:36.752 --> 23:42.192
笙ｪI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see笙ｪ

23:43.025 --> 23:47.632
笙ｪSee the world and how it flows.
We never let go笙ｪ

23:49.712 --> 23:52.464
笙ｪSo I'll take my time笙ｪ

23:52.976 --> 23:55.824
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

23:56.208 --> 24:00.336
笙ｪThe love that I should deserve笙ｪ

24:02.613 --> 24:05.200
笙ｪWhen the time is right笙ｪ

24:06.909 --> 24:07.469
Yan.

24:11.469 --> 24:12.068
Mr. Gao.

24:12.869 --> 24:13.949
Grandma said

24:14.108 --> 24:15.869
you went to work
as a tailor in the city.

24:16.389 --> 24:17.548
Why did you come back?

24:18.068 --> 24:19.469
That was years ago.

24:19.709 --> 24:21.429
Our village is better than the city now.

24:21.869 --> 24:23.788
I started a small orchard,

24:24.229 --> 24:25.189
opened a tavern,

24:25.469 --> 24:26.629
and leased a fishing pond.

24:26.869 --> 24:29.268
I sometimes host fruit-picking groups

24:29.828 --> 24:30.832
and fishing enthusiasts.

24:31.108 --> 24:32.828
City folks' money is easy to earn.

24:33.429 --> 24:34.748
That sounds great.

24:36.149 --> 24:36.548
Yan.

24:36.909 --> 24:39.149
Are you still a chef in the city?

24:39.989 --> 24:40.389
I...

24:41.348 --> 24:43.229
I'm not a chef.

24:43.629 --> 24:45.268
I run a food show.

24:46.429 --> 24:47.508
A food show.

24:47.669 --> 24:49.308
- Like those on TV?
- Yeah.

24:50.229 --> 24:53.028
Do you really eat the food you make?

24:53.149 --> 24:55.508
I'll contact you if we need fruits.

24:56.080 --> 24:57.360
You know me well.

24:59.709 --> 25:01.308
- Thanks, Mr. Gao.
- No problem.

25:36.308 --> 25:36.788
Grandma.

25:37.469 --> 25:38.268
You're back.

25:38.469 --> 25:40.389
Why didn't you call first?

25:40.828 --> 25:41.588
Come on.

25:41.748 --> 25:42.548
- Be careful.
- It's fine.

25:42.669 --> 25:43.268
I got this.

25:43.429 --> 25:44.149
Alright.

25:45.348 --> 25:45.788
Alright.

25:46.068 --> 25:47.709
It looks so dangerous.

25:48.548 --> 25:50.548
What's so dangerous about it?

25:51.189 --> 25:52.348
Alright.

25:53.869 --> 25:55.068
Let me do it. Sit down.

25:55.429 --> 25:56.588
There's been more rain

25:56.629 --> 25:58.149
and it's been colder this year.

25:58.588 --> 25:59.949
I'm worried

25:59.949 --> 26:01.429
these osmanthus flowers

26:02.028 --> 26:03.149
won't get picked in time.

26:03.229 --> 26:04.629
Then we won't get to make

26:04.669 --> 26:06.028
nice osmanthus jam.

26:06.508 --> 26:07.949
I'll pick them. Don't worry.

26:08.108 --> 26:08.949
Just sit tight.

26:09.709 --> 26:11.108
Didn't I tell you?

26:11.748 --> 26:12.869
When no one's home,

26:12.949 --> 26:14.068
don't stand so high up.

26:14.068 --> 26:15.028
It's dangerous.

26:15.268 --> 26:16.869
But I'm using the stool.

26:17.548 --> 26:18.828
That's even worse.

26:22.669 --> 26:23.989
You're still good at this.

26:25.949 --> 26:26.588
You remember.

26:26.788 --> 26:27.828
Of course.

26:28.229 --> 26:29.389
How could I forget the skills

26:29.588 --> 26:30.268
you taught me?

26:34.828 --> 26:35.709
Is everything okay?

26:35.828 --> 26:36.588
Yeah.

26:36.788 --> 26:37.389
Really?

26:37.508 --> 26:39.268
It's even better now that you're back.

26:42.588 --> 26:43.348
Yan.

26:43.348 --> 26:46.308
I learned how to make pan-seared cod.

26:46.669 --> 26:48.548
I'll cook it for you next time.

26:50.189 --> 26:51.508
Why don't you try

26:51.508 --> 26:55.028
the mixed fruit platter
I made for you first?

26:55.709 --> 26:56.028
Here.

26:56.989 --> 26:57.548
My child.

26:58.028 --> 26:58.869
It's a huge plate.

26:58.869 --> 27:00.669
Can we finish all this?

27:01.028 --> 27:01.669
No worries.

27:01.788 --> 27:03.229
We can put them in the fridge.

27:05.788 --> 27:06.268
Sweet, huh?

27:12.709 --> 27:15.669
This apple must be homegrown.

27:16.028 --> 27:17.548
Homegrown apples are the best.

27:19.548 --> 27:20.028
So tasty.

27:23.229 --> 27:23.748
Grandma.

27:24.548 --> 27:26.028
Remember that boyfriend

27:26.028 --> 27:27.508
I told you about?

27:28.788 --> 27:29.469
Of course.

27:29.909 --> 27:30.989
You mention him

27:31.028 --> 27:31.909
every time you call.

27:32.469 --> 27:33.748
Things are going well.

27:35.189 --> 27:36.949
I've met his family.

27:37.588 --> 27:38.869
So we're planning

27:39.588 --> 27:41.429
to get married next month.

27:45.788 --> 27:47.068
How could you keep

27:47.068 --> 27:48.949
such happy news from me until now?

27:52.389 --> 27:53.229
Yan,

27:55.989 --> 27:57.709
I've finally lived to see you

27:58.108 --> 27:59.709
getting married.

28:01.348 --> 28:03.548
I've been waiting for this moment.

28:05.348 --> 28:06.548
I'm so happy.

28:14.189 --> 28:14.909
What's wrong?

28:18.189 --> 28:19.389
Is something bothering you?

28:27.348 --> 28:27.869
I knew it.

28:28.508 --> 28:29.949
Nothing escapes you.

28:34.229 --> 28:35.389
Mom and Dad went to Jingzhou.

28:40.869 --> 28:41.949
You know that

28:43.828 --> 28:45.828
I've never been close to them.

28:47.389 --> 28:49.268
So I don't want them at my wedding.

28:49.909 --> 28:51.909
I won't invite them.

28:52.989 --> 28:54.469
But if I tell them that,

28:55.028 --> 28:56.389
given Dad's temper,

28:57.828 --> 28:58.989
he'll make trouble.

29:01.189 --> 29:03.028
But my wedding's next month...

29:05.748 --> 29:06.389
Grandma.

29:07.348 --> 29:08.828
I know what to do.

29:09.709 --> 29:12.108
I'll ask them to come back.

29:13.709 --> 29:15.828
They won't go there again.

29:19.028 --> 29:19.629
Yan,

29:21.629 --> 29:23.949
you've been struggling
in the city alone.

29:24.709 --> 29:26.748
I know better than anyone

29:28.229 --> 29:29.669
how much you've suffered.

29:31.348 --> 29:31.989
So

29:32.629 --> 29:34.069
your wedding

29:35.248 --> 29:36.949
will be

29:37.989 --> 29:39.068
proper,

29:39.308 --> 29:40.348
splendid,

29:41.709 --> 29:42.989
and beautiful.

30:00.508 --> 30:01.108
Grandma,

30:05.629 --> 30:06.989
Jingzhou's too far.

30:11.869 --> 30:13.068
It's a huge trip for you.

30:20.508 --> 30:21.469
Exactly.

30:21.669 --> 30:23.788
You know I've aged.

30:24.068 --> 30:25.949
With these old legs,

30:26.068 --> 30:28.108
traveling all the way

30:28.389 --> 30:29.389
back and forth...

30:29.989 --> 30:30.909
I can't do it.

30:31.229 --> 30:33.469
My bones would rattle apart.

30:34.108 --> 30:34.909
Yan.

30:35.308 --> 30:35.828
Really.

30:36.389 --> 30:38.629
I won't go to Jingzhou.

30:38.709 --> 30:40.268
After the wedding,

30:40.629 --> 30:42.189
keep a copy of your wedding photo.

30:42.348 --> 30:45.748
Bring it when you visit again.

30:46.068 --> 30:46.508
Okay?

30:46.629 --> 30:47.709
I'll hang it in my room

30:47.788 --> 30:49.028
and see you kids every day.

30:50.068 --> 30:52.108
That'll make me happy.

30:54.189 --> 30:57.709
I can't travel with these old legs.

30:57.828 --> 30:58.508
At night,

30:58.629 --> 30:59.748
they swell up.

31:00.028 --> 31:00.828
Imagine me

31:01.028 --> 31:02.548
in a strange city,

31:03.308 --> 31:05.389
while you're celebrating...

31:05.828 --> 31:07.108
If I fall ill there,

31:07.268 --> 31:09.108
I'd cause you so much trouble.

31:09.469 --> 31:10.429
No, I won't go there.

31:10.629 --> 31:11.508
I'm not going.

31:11.588 --> 31:12.588
I'll stay

31:12.788 --> 31:14.709
and wait for your good news.

31:15.508 --> 31:17.629
What if I end up...

31:20.909 --> 31:21.788
You'll be overwhelmed.

31:21.788 --> 31:22.949
Sit tight.

31:23.788 --> 31:25.828
Really. I...

31:26.429 --> 31:27.268
Look.

31:27.429 --> 31:28.788
Every night,

31:28.869 --> 31:30.268
my legs swell up.

31:30.308 --> 31:30.949
Press here.

31:31.229 --> 31:32.189
It sinks right in.

31:32.788 --> 31:34.028
Stop massaging me.

31:34.709 --> 31:35.469
Just a bit more.

31:35.669 --> 31:36.469
Come on.

31:37.989 --> 31:38.748
That's enough.

31:39.669 --> 31:41.469
Should I prepare a foot bath for you?

31:41.909 --> 31:42.828
Alright.

32:43.869 --> 32:46.588
Aren't you putting fruit in the fridge?

32:46.629 --> 32:47.308
Why...

32:51.189 --> 32:52.949
Why are you crying?

32:54.548 --> 32:55.508
What's wrong?

32:58.909 --> 32:59.588
What happened?

33:03.389 --> 33:05.348
I haven't been home for so long.

33:07.469 --> 33:09.828
I can't finish all this osmanthus jam.

33:11.108 --> 33:12.909
Do you know why I've been making

33:12.949 --> 33:14.508
so much sweet osmanthus jam for you

33:14.508 --> 33:15.989
since you were a kid?

33:16.229 --> 33:17.508
I wanted to fill your heart

33:17.828 --> 33:19.108
with sweetness,

33:19.389 --> 33:22.108
so you could face all the hardships.

33:22.989 --> 33:23.828
Stop crying.

33:24.629 --> 33:25.909
Don't cry.

33:27.788 --> 33:29.108
My poor baby.

33:30.629 --> 33:31.508
Stop crying now.

33:31.669 --> 33:32.308
Don't cry.

33:34.704 --> 33:36.528
笙ｪSuch real connections笙ｪ

33:37.869 --> 33:40.028
I promise I'll bring you to Jingzhou.

33:43.189 --> 33:45.548
I'll make sure you live a good life.

33:46.508 --> 33:46.989
Okay.

33:49.348 --> 33:50.748
I'll be looking forward to it.

33:50.813 --> 33:54.192
笙ｪThere's no reason
not to lose control for this笙ｪ

33:54.510 --> 33:56.496
笙ｪAll the year round笙ｪ

33:57.508 --> 33:58.308
It's alright.

33:58.788 --> 33:59.508
Stop crying.

34:02.064 --> 34:04.112
笙ｪSee the converging stars笙ｪ

34:04.408 --> 34:06.480
笙ｪAs lucky as we are笙ｪ

34:06.960 --> 34:09.072
笙ｪTwo passionate hearts are笙ｪ

34:09.424 --> 34:11.952
笙ｪIn perfect harmony笙ｪ

34:12.160 --> 34:14.192
笙ｪSince the day I met you笙ｪ

34:14.512 --> 34:16.528
笙ｪI've been looking forward to each trip笙ｪ

34:17.008 --> 34:19.120
笙ｪWe can go anywhere笙ｪ

34:21.588 --> 34:22.028
Alright.

34:22.269 --> 34:22.628
Here.

34:24.269 --> 34:25.668
Your dirty little hands.

34:26.429 --> 34:26.949
This time,

34:27.148 --> 34:28.469
how did your exams go?

34:28.869 --> 34:30.949
I got first in the class again.

34:31.228 --> 34:31.989
Dig in.

34:32.068 --> 34:33.028
First place again.

34:33.909 --> 34:36.068
That makes me so happy.

34:36.469 --> 34:37.068
Thumbs up.

34:37.269 --> 34:38.028
You're amazing.

34:38.469 --> 34:38.989
Grandma,

34:39.389 --> 34:40.869
the osmanthus cake is amazing.

34:44.586 --> 34:46.683
笙ｪSee the converging stars笙ｪ

34:48.909 --> 34:49.588
Yan,

34:51.548 --> 34:52.469
listen to me.

34:54.469 --> 34:56.349
Considering our family background,

34:56.909 --> 34:58.548
studying hard is

34:59.148 --> 35:00.349
your only way out.

35:00.869 --> 35:01.628
Studying hard

35:02.829 --> 35:05.028
is your only way to change your life.

35:06.068 --> 35:06.869
You hear me?

35:08.508 --> 35:09.869
Grandma, have some too.

35:10.548 --> 35:11.228
Alright.

35:11.909 --> 35:12.269
Okay.

35:13.588 --> 35:14.228
Grandma.

35:15.668 --> 35:17.508
My sweet granddaughter

35:17.829 --> 35:19.469
is calling me.

35:20.108 --> 35:20.789
What's wrong?

35:21.228 --> 35:21.749
Look.

35:21.828 --> 35:24.176
笙ｪI've been looking forward to each trip笙ｪ

35:24.829 --> 35:25.349
Yan.

35:25.508 --> 35:26.749
I knew you could do it.

35:27.108 --> 35:28.508
You made it.

35:28.668 --> 35:29.989
(Jingzhou Communication University Admission Letter)
The red booklet.

35:29.989 --> 35:31.148
Your dream came true.

35:32.028 --> 35:33.469
Come here.

35:40.087 --> 35:44.656
(Certificate)

35:50.749 --> 35:51.429
Yan,

35:53.749 --> 35:55.829
I've saved some money for you.

35:56.469 --> 35:57.668
The password is your birthday.

35:57.949 --> 35:58.429
Take it.

35:58.829 --> 35:59.508
I don't need it.

36:00.389 --> 36:02.869
I've saved enough for college expenses.

36:02.989 --> 36:05.068
Besides, you've already paid my tuition.

36:07.068 --> 36:07.749
Yan,

36:08.068 --> 36:09.068
listen to me.

36:09.829 --> 36:11.949
Don't you love dancing

36:12.108 --> 36:13.188
and playing instruments?

36:13.429 --> 36:14.508
I heard universities have

36:14.909 --> 36:16.548
many extracurricular classes too.

36:16.789 --> 36:17.909
You'll need money.

36:18.349 --> 36:20.108
You'll need to find some teachers.

36:20.508 --> 36:22.508
More skills never hurt anyone.

36:22.869 --> 36:23.188
Here.

36:23.749 --> 36:24.349
Take it.

36:25.712 --> 36:27.728
笙ｪSeparated笙ｪ

36:29.744 --> 36:32.732
笙ｪLike the world shook off its dust笙ｪ

36:35.749 --> 36:36.789
Silly child.

36:37.215 --> 36:39.188
笙ｪIn the crowd笙ｪ

36:39.188 --> 36:40.708
Why are you crying?

36:42.389 --> 36:44.349
You're going to Jingzhou.

36:44.708 --> 36:46.588
How amazing is that?

36:47.349 --> 36:48.228
Right?

36:49.469 --> 36:50.469
You've made it.

36:51.628 --> 36:53.628
You've accomplished it.

36:53.909 --> 36:55.749
You should be happy.

36:57.389 --> 36:57.909
Listen.

36:59.389 --> 37:01.148
When you arrive in Jingzhou,

37:01.469 --> 37:03.028
visit the canal,

37:03.349 --> 37:04.909
go to Longquan Gate

37:05.108 --> 37:05.869
and the Yun Palace.

37:06.708 --> 37:09.309
Take lots of photos

37:09.708 --> 37:10.869
and send them to me.

37:10.949 --> 37:12.188
Show me the photos.

37:13.068 --> 37:13.989
I'll be so happy.

37:14.749 --> 37:16.269
Don't cry.

37:17.269 --> 37:18.668
Don't cry.

37:19.668 --> 37:21.108
Don't cry.

37:21.989 --> 37:23.429
You're still like a child.

37:23.789 --> 37:25.469
You should be happy.

37:26.429 --> 37:28.708
Yan, we should be happy.

37:28.869 --> 37:29.469
Stop crying.

37:30.148 --> 37:33.349
Stop crying. You're making me sad.

37:34.789 --> 37:35.949
Let me help you pack.

37:36.708 --> 37:38.668
Keep the card somewhere safe.

37:38.749 --> 37:39.588
Don't lose it.

37:41.508 --> 37:42.508
Let's close this.

37:45.588 --> 37:45.989
(Grandma,)

37:45.989 --> 37:48.068
(I'll make a lot of money)

37:50.469 --> 37:51.502
(and take care of you.)

37:51.502 --> 37:54.035
笙ｪLife existed without you here笙ｪ

37:54.176 --> 37:57.322
笙ｪHappy with or without you笙ｪ

37:57.328 --> 37:59.792
笙ｪWhy am I missing a piece of soul笙ｪ

38:00.749 --> 38:02.469
Would you like to try some milk?

38:02.469 --> 38:03.989
It contains lactoferrin.

38:04.028 --> 38:05.228
We have a promotion today.

38:05.429 --> 38:06.320
Buy two, get one free.

38:06.429 --> 38:07.148
If you like it,

38:07.148 --> 38:08.068
please take a look.

38:08.429 --> 38:09.548
Here, try some milk.

38:09.789 --> 38:10.949
Here's the flyer.

38:11.188 --> 38:12.869
Please take it. Thank you.

38:14.548 --> 38:15.668
Your beers.

38:15.989 --> 38:16.909
No ice, right?

38:18.588 --> 38:19.228
Your beers.

38:19.508 --> 38:20.028
Three people?

38:20.749 --> 38:21.429
One more, right?

38:21.429 --> 38:22.349
We'd like to order.

38:22.429 --> 38:22.989
Coming.

38:23.148 --> 38:24.708
According to the triangle's

38:24.789 --> 38:26.108
internal angle sum theorem,

38:26.708 --> 38:27.228
it's...

38:27.389 --> 38:30.668
We can conclude that
the known angle equals angle C.

38:32.429 --> 38:33.389
Half of 70 degrees.

38:33.588 --> 38:34.228
It's 35 degrees.

38:34.829 --> 38:35.829
Buy two, get one free.

38:35.989 --> 38:36.628
If you like it,

38:36.628 --> 38:37.148
take a look.

38:37.349 --> 38:39.909
It's great for children as breakfast.

38:40.848 --> 38:43.664
笙ｪYour trust笙ｪ

38:44.166 --> 38:46.640
笙ｪLook back once more笙ｪ

38:48.949 --> 38:49.429
Hello.

38:49.588 --> 38:50.628
Try some milk.

38:50.909 --> 38:52.789
It contains lactoferrin.

38:52.789 --> 38:53.668
Thirteen processes.

38:53.829 --> 38:55.548
- What would you like?
- Four squid skewers.

38:56.309 --> 38:57.708
- Four chicken wings.
- One second.

38:57.708 --> 38:58.949
Excuse me. Three beers.

38:59.269 --> 39:00.269
Take these glasses away.

39:01.349 --> 39:02.228
Do you have seats?

39:02.588 --> 39:03.588
Yeah, right this way.

39:04.016 --> 39:07.056
笙ｪReside in my heart笙ｪ

39:07.440 --> 39:09.392
笙ｪAdmit loneliness笙ｪ

39:09.776 --> 39:12.372
笙ｪWait for travelers' return笙ｪ

39:12.789 --> 39:13.508
Yan.

39:13.668 --> 39:15.028
Yan, come here.

39:15.344 --> 39:17.829
笙ｪI'll repay you tomorrow笙ｪ

39:17.829 --> 39:18.749
Coming right away.

39:19.056 --> 39:21.008
笙ｪYou're my true love笙ｪ

39:21.246 --> 39:23.440
笙ｪI realize when I lose you笙ｪ

39:24.909 --> 39:25.349
That's it.

39:25.349 --> 39:26.068
Take a look.

39:26.068 --> 39:26.909
What would you like?

39:27.309 --> 39:28.668
We have signature dishes here.

39:29.269 --> 39:30.108
This is not spicy.

39:30.269 --> 39:31.148
This one is spicy.

39:31.188 --> 39:32.708
- Do you eat spicy food?
- Yeah.

39:32.708 --> 39:33.068
Okay.

39:33.668 --> 39:34.469
Check these out.

39:35.429 --> 39:38.028
Ms. Xu, here is
this month's tutoring fee.

39:38.749 --> 39:40.749
I'm very pleased
with your trial class today.

39:40.829 --> 39:42.628
I hope you'll be tutoring my kid.

39:44.708 --> 39:45.829
Rest assured.

39:45.949 --> 39:47.588
I'll teach Yingying well.

39:47.949 --> 39:48.909
Thank you.

40:04.949 --> 40:05.469
Miss.

40:05.668 --> 40:06.389
Need a taxi?

40:07.148 --> 40:08.068
Need a taxi?

40:10.588 --> 40:11.309
Stop checking.

40:11.588 --> 40:12.789
No buses at this hour.

40:13.309 --> 40:14.269
There's still one bus.

40:14.469 --> 40:15.108
Thanks.

40:15.309 --> 40:15.909
I'm fine.

40:18.188 --> 40:19.188
Sir, are you available?

40:19.469 --> 40:20.068
Yeah.

40:34.028 --> 40:34.949
Hi, Grandma.

40:36.508 --> 40:37.349
Yan.

40:38.108 --> 40:38.749
Yan.

40:38.829 --> 40:40.829
Why did you send me money again?

40:40.989 --> 40:43.548
I can't spend this much money.

40:43.949 --> 40:45.708
You're studying away from home.

40:46.108 --> 40:48.068
There must be lots of expenses.

40:48.188 --> 40:50.188
Eat properly.

40:51.309 --> 40:52.708
Drink more milk.

40:52.909 --> 40:53.989
Eat more eggs.

40:54.269 --> 40:55.829
And... what's it called?

40:56.188 --> 40:57.148
Vitamins.

40:57.668 --> 40:58.708
Take those too.

40:59.148 --> 40:59.628
Right?

40:59.989 --> 41:00.708
I know.

41:00.949 --> 41:02.269
My current part-time job

41:02.269 --> 41:03.188
pays pretty well.

41:03.188 --> 41:04.668
Plus, I found a new one today

41:04.708 --> 41:05.469
with better pay.

41:05.469 --> 41:06.188
Rest assured.

41:06.309 --> 41:08.789
Just have fun at home
and wait for me to go back

41:08.909 --> 41:10.108
during winter break.

41:12.188 --> 41:12.628
Well...

41:12.829 --> 41:14.389
I-I'm waiting for the bus.

41:14.508 --> 41:15.309
I'll call you later.

41:15.548 --> 41:17.349
Okay, be safe.

41:18.708 --> 41:19.469
Okay, bye.

41:46.389 --> 41:48.108
Look, it's snowing.

41:48.668 --> 41:50.469
A timely snow promises a good harvest.

41:52.188 --> 41:53.869
Careful. Don't get burned.

41:56.188 --> 41:57.949
The fireworks look amazing.

42:19.068 --> 42:19.668
(Grandma,)

42:20.269 --> 42:21.469
(after I get a job)

42:21.749 --> 42:23.028
(and establish myself,)

42:23.429 --> 42:24.789
(I'll bring you to Jingzhou.)

42:24.789 --> 42:27.389
(We'll live together
and never be apart again.)

42:28.188 --> 42:29.588
(If my future boyfriend)

42:29.869 --> 42:30.909
(objects to this,)

42:30.989 --> 42:31.949
(I'll dump him.)

42:32.708 --> 42:34.028
(When I get married,)

42:34.028 --> 42:35.429
(you'll sit at the head table.)

42:36.309 --> 42:37.389
(Great plan.)

42:37.429 --> 42:38.989
(I'll follow your lead.)

42:58.389 --> 42:59.068
Do you like it?

43:04.592 --> 43:05.469
Let me put it on you.

43:24.869 --> 43:25.989
(I told myself that)

43:26.628 --> 43:28.588
(only through diligence and hard work)

43:28.989 --> 43:29.989
(can I overcome)

43:29.989 --> 43:31.749
(one mountain after another.)

43:32.628 --> 43:34.148
(Only by becoming strong)

43:34.309 --> 43:35.829
(can I achieve permanent success.)

43:36.708 --> 43:38.349
(Only by achieving all goals)

43:39.188 --> 43:41.068
(can I make up for all my mistakes)

43:41.869 --> 43:42.508
(and make up)

43:43.269 --> 43:44.548
(to those I've let down.)

44:08.309 --> 44:09.789
Is the risk analysis

44:10.389 --> 44:11.708
on Plot 178 ready?

44:12.068 --> 44:12.668
Mr. Shen.

44:13.949 --> 44:14.749
I'm Fang Lei.

44:15.269 --> 44:16.429
I'll present

44:16.469 --> 44:17.508
the risk assessment report

44:17.588 --> 44:18.548
on Plot 178.

44:20.188 --> 44:20.588
Mr. Shen,

44:20.909 --> 44:23.148
she's new to the investment
strategy department.

44:29.989 --> 44:30.588
Let's start.

44:32.148 --> 44:34.389
There are four major
risks for this plot.

44:34.588 --> 44:35.108
First,

44:35.548 --> 44:36.389
the auctioned land

44:36.548 --> 44:37.989
has existing encumbrances.

44:38.508 --> 44:39.909
There are two bank mortgages

44:40.188 --> 44:41.309
and objection registrations.

44:41.668 --> 44:42.588
If we don't clarify

44:42.749 --> 44:44.668
property rights before bidding,

44:45.028 --> 44:47.269
they might eventually become our debts.

44:48.028 --> 44:48.508
Second,

44:48.869 --> 44:51.028
according to the government's
new planning policy,

44:51.508 --> 44:52.749
the land's lease term

44:53.068 --> 44:54.309
may be adjusted.

45:01.389 --> 45:01.989
Lisa.

45:02.108 --> 45:02.469
Bye.

45:02.588 --> 45:02.989
Let's go.

45:05.309 --> 45:06.269
Fang Lei, see you.

45:06.628 --> 45:07.668
- Bye.
- Bye.

45:08.588 --> 45:09.269
Bye, Mr. Shen.

45:09.389 --> 45:09.909
Bye.

45:10.389 --> 45:10.989
Mr. Shen.

45:16.389 --> 45:18.869
Why did you suddenly come back

45:19.269 --> 45:20.188
and join our company?

45:20.628 --> 45:21.989
Isn't it a pleasant surprise

45:22.668 --> 45:23.829
for you?

45:25.548 --> 45:27.188
Or perhaps you are not happy

45:28.188 --> 45:29.108
to see me?

45:30.668 --> 45:32.989
You have to readjust to many things.

45:33.829 --> 45:35.749
If I have any problems at work,

45:36.228 --> 45:37.429
can I consult you?

45:38.869 --> 45:40.148
The HR policies require you

45:40.469 --> 45:42.028
to report to your direct supervisor.

45:43.628 --> 45:44.749
I was just kidding.

45:46.429 --> 45:46.989
Haoming.

45:48.309 --> 45:49.548
Do you remember this jacket?

45:55.749 --> 45:56.789
You won this as a prize

45:57.148 --> 45:58.749
at the collegiate kayak championship

45:58.789 --> 45:59.869
during your sophomore year.

46:00.668 --> 46:01.668
I said I liked it,

46:01.749 --> 46:03.508
and you gave it to me
without hesitation.

46:03.909 --> 46:04.749
I was so happy.

46:05.068 --> 46:06.869
So I took this photo as a memento.

46:08.389 --> 46:09.389
I didn't give it to you.

46:09.869 --> 46:10.789
You snatched it.

46:12.588 --> 46:13.588
So you remember.

46:16.749 --> 46:18.789
I remember everything you said, too.

46:20.309 --> 46:22.469
When you left London, you told me

46:23.628 --> 46:25.028
to focus on my studies there

46:25.588 --> 46:27.508
and return after graduation.

46:28.749 --> 46:29.349
Now,

46:30.909 --> 46:31.668
I'm back.

46:48.990 --> 46:50.800
笙ｪLike fireworks that loved笙ｪ

46:50.832 --> 46:52.464
笙ｪRushing toward the stars笙ｪ

46:52.464 --> 46:54.480
笙ｪUndaunted by pain笙ｪ

46:55.536 --> 46:57.424
笙ｪFearless of flames笙ｪ

46:57.424 --> 47:01.008
笙ｪEven if just a fleeting sparkle笙ｪ

47:02.064 --> 47:03.984
笙ｪWe shed tears笙ｪ

47:03.984 --> 47:07.568
笙ｪDeep blue seas turn to foam笙ｪ

47:07.760 --> 47:10.512
笙ｪWe regained freedom笙ｪ

47:11.632 --> 47:14.320
笙ｪIf you remember me笙ｪ

47:14.320 --> 47:17.479
笙ｪThen I'm pleased笙ｪ

47:30.496 --> 47:34.640
笙ｪI just wanna take my time tonight笙ｪ

47:36.641 --> 47:40.931
笙ｪTo do all the things I said I'd try笙ｪ

47:42.656 --> 47:48.512
笙ｪI go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different place笙ｪ

47:48.992 --> 47:51.808
笙ｪI go drink, go party, and go dance笙ｪ

47:51.808 --> 47:55.136
笙ｪEven if I'm lonely笙ｪ

47:55.776 --> 48:00.512
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
too many times笙ｪ

48:02.284 --> 48:06.522
笙ｪI'm giving it all to get nothing back笙ｪ

48:08.384 --> 48:13.536
笙ｪI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see笙ｪ

48:14.624 --> 48:19.486
笙ｪSee the world and how it flows.
We never let go笙ｪ

48:21.216 --> 48:24.192
笙ｪSo I'll take my time笙ｪ

48:24.416 --> 48:27.584
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

48:27.584 --> 48:32.609
笙ｪThe love I should deserve笙ｪ

48:34.251 --> 48:37.257
笙ｪWhen the time is right笙ｪ

48:37.257 --> 48:40.534
笙ｪYou realize笙ｪ

48:40.534 --> 48:45.164
笙ｪIt will all be alright笙ｪ

48:46.912 --> 48:51.596
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
